269 General Assembly having cognizance of matters relating to children not
270 later than March 1, 2017, and every two years thereafter; [and]
271 (13) Prepare an in-depth report on the treatment needs and stability
272 of placement for children in Specialized Trauma-Informed Treatment
273 Assessment and Reunification homes, group homes and residential
274 facilities, by reviewing a sampling of children in such placements with
275 emphasis on (A) information on child welfare histories, (B) the number
